headline: Does AutoZone Still Offer Value After Multi Year Surge And Recent Pullback?
summary: If you are wondering whether AutoZone is still a smart buy after its substantial multi year run, or if the easier gains are behind it, you are not alone. We are going to examine what the market is really pricing in. Despite a strong long term track record, with the share price up roughly 196.5% over five years and 46.1% over three years, the stock has pulled back recently. It has slipped 8.6% over the last week and 6.0% over the last month, while still sitting about 7.6% higher year to date...
